      "body" : "> Though, 10.8+ is only required for our binary distribution, 10.7 works fine if you self-compile.\r\n\r\nDoes it? If 10.7's C++11 libraries are broken, how can it?",
      "created_at" : "2016-10-27T06:51:18Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/9022#issuecomment-256560993",
      "id" : 256560993,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/9022",
