      "body" : "> Does it? If 10.7's C++11 libraries are broken, how can it?\r\n\r\nIMO its a ABI difference. We compile against 10.9's c++ libraries which probably must have ABI differences to 10.7 ones.\r\nBut better ask @theuni to be certain.",
      "created_at" : "2016-10-28T12:02:39Z",
