      "body" : "Hacky but makes sense. We do a similar thing for glibc compat configure\nflag. In the case of ancient OSX it's not worth it though, OSX users seem\nto have an extremely high update acceptance, no need to support a 5 year\nold OS (wish we could say the same of windows)\n",
